    "In contrast, DL can inspire researchers and assist them in efficiently designing algorithms.",
    "Furthermore, DL, adept at modeling intricate functions, has the potential to supplant cumbersome computations in traditional algorithms.",
    "This replacement not only expedites the computational process but also furnishes supplementary information or decision criteria for traditional algorithms [24].Additionally, the rise of large language model (LLM) has introduced new possibilities for TSP algorithm design.",
    "LLMs can leverage vast amounts of data and learned knowledge to automatically generate and refine heuristics.",
    "This capability allows for the exploration of a broader heuristic space without being constrained by human-designed components."
